<p>Features&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>free and compulsory education for 6-14&nbsp;</li>
<li>25% reservation for EWS</li>
<li>Fixed TSR (teacher student ratio)&nbsp;</li>
<li>school infra&nbsp;</li>
<li>sharing of finances between centre and state&nbsp;</li></ol>
<p>Analysis - GOOD&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>Section 12 of RTE =&gt; 25% =&gt; education for all + social integration&nbsp;</li>
<li>upper primary GER up</li>
<li>sanitation infra improved&nbsp;</li></ol>
<p>LACKING&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>Infra =&gt; 13% schools fulfill RTE infra norms (U-DISE data)&nbsp;</li>
<li>state wise discrepancy in GER&nbsp;</li>
<li>CWSN (children with special needs) left out of RTE&nbsp;</li>
<li>RTE is input oriented&nbsp;</li>
<li>quality of learning outcome?&nbsp;</li>
<li># trained teachers ?&nbsp;</li></ol>